{"tid":1134129,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"隨波圖操練心臟病發　37歲卡斯拿斯送院後情況穩定","createTime":"2019-05-01T14:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T14:57:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45a8f8038571d00ac14e4d8346a62134e2870122","tid":1134129,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190501/large/1556722230_8126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190501%2Flarge%2F1556722230_8126.jpg&h=911b33e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年屆37歲的前皇家馬德里門將卡斯拿斯，周三跟隨現時效力球會波圖操練時心臟病發，馬上被送往當地醫院治理，波圖及後發出聲明，指這位曾替西班牙國家隊贏得一屆世盃及兩屆歐國盃的門將情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n波圖向葡萄牙媒體TVI證實聖卡斯心臟病發送院的消息，但指這位門將情況穩定，進展不錯，但預計會進行更詳細的檢查，今季餘下賽事料不會再披甲。<br />\n<br />\n卡斯拿斯與拍拖多年的西班牙電視女主播莎拉，在2015年成婚，現育有兩名兒子，而這位門將除了替狂牛軍團奪得一屆世盃及兩屆歐國盃外，亦為皇馬捧得3座歐聯及5座西甲聯賽錦標。2015年轉投波圖後，職業生涯也添多一座葡超錦標，今屆歐聯助球隊殺入歐聯八強，可惜最後大敗給利物浦出局。"},{"pid":"b38792556eed048f799f79eded15c09a3b052ff5","tid":1134129,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:56:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190501/59552708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190501%2F59552708&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmeUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=70cd601f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190501%2F59552708&h=1019ff89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190501/59552708</a>"},{"pid":"d1558f423ffa4f095226f69b0e8b3ba2860fd15a","tid":1134129,"uid":85934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"蘋果記者將個topic 打到死撚咗咁"},{"pid":"ab0865bdb9c616e77852af0b3010b1c917be6104","tid":1134129,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply